===Pronunciation===
בּעל זבוּב / ba‛al zebûb / bah'-al zeb-oob'

===Etymology===
From [[בּעל]] {{HH|1168}} and [[זבוּב]] {{HH|2070}}; Baal of (the) Fly; Baal Zebub, a special deity of the Ekronites

===Proper noun===
'''בּעל זבוּב'''

# Baal-zebub.

